\begin_layout Enumerate
We form
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
M^{1}=A\otimes B=\sum_{i,j,l,m}A_{ij}B_{lm}e_{ijlm},
\]

\end_inset

which is a 4-dimensional array whose generic element in position 
\begin_inset Formula $i,j,l,m$
\end_inset

