\begin_inset Formula $A_{ij}B_{lm}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
We fuse the second and third dimensions, corresponding to the indices 
\begin_inset Formula $j$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $l$
\end_inset

