\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
This lets us express the usual matrix product as
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
AB & =\left(\sum_{k}A_{ik}B_{km}\middle|im\right)\\
 & =(A_{ik}B_{km}\mid im)\\
 & =A\myodot{\overline{2}}1B.
\end{align*}

\end_inset

The 
\emph on
