\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\nabla_{X}f=-U^{T}V^{T}=-X^{-T}A^{T}B^{T}X^{-T}
\]

\end_inset

Note that we simplified expression
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:simpl_express"

\end_inset

